headline: Coca-Cola Consolidated: Q1 Earnings Snapshot
summary: CHARLOTTE, N.C. (AP) — Coca-Cola Consolidated, Inc. COKE) on Wednesday reported earnings of $103.6 million in its first quarter. On a per-share basis, the Charlotte, North Carolina-based company said it had net income of $11.87.
